						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Ballāḷa III. Undated. (A.D. 1291-1342.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Unfinished and mentions a long list of titles of the king. Lord of Tuvarāpati, the hero of mountain fort, the destroyer of the Makara kingdom, the restorer of the Chōḻa kingdom, the peace maker of the Pāṇḍyas and the destroyer of Kāḍavakula are some of the titiles listed.</p>						

						<p>Published in <hi rend="italic">E.C.</hi> (n), Vol. IV, No. Kol. 96.</p>						

